racegenders.config_desc: Though shorter and slimmer than humans, elves are most easily identified by their pronounced, pointed ears. They have a reputation for being dignified and a bit aloof.

racegenders.name: halfElfMale
racegenders.config_desc: Half-elves have both human and elven parentage and take traits from both races. They have shorter ears than elves but are longer-lived than humans and share their inquisitive and adventurous nature.

racegenders.name: halfElfFemale
racegenders.config_desc: Half-elves have both human and elven parentage and take traits from both races. They have shorter ears than elves but are longer-lived than humans and share their inquisitive and adventurous nature.

racegenders.name: dwarfMale
racegenders.config_desc: Dwarves are a hardy race, identifiable by their stout, strong stature and large, round ears. The males are also known for their impressive beards. They make excellent fighters and tireless workers. Dwarves can be wary of other races at first, but make fiercely loyal friends and allies.

racegenders.name: dwarfFemale
racegenders.config_desc: Dwarves are a hardy race, identifiable by their stout, strong stature and large, round ears. They make excellent fighters and tireless workers. Dwarves can be wary of other races at first, but make fiercely loyal friends and allies.

racegenders.name: elementalMale
racegenders.config_desc: With elemental magic in their blood, these humanoids are uniquely in touch with the primal powers of the world. racegenders.name: gnomeMale
racegenders.config_desc: Gnomes are tiny, slender creatures. They have large noses and long, pointed ears that stick out from their heads. They are known for being remarkably quick-witted and a bit mischievous.

racegenders.name: gnomeFemale
racegenders.config_desc: Gnomes are tiny, slender creatures. They have large noses and long, pointed ears that stick out from their heads. They are known for being remarkably quick-witted and a bit mischievous.

racegenders.name: halfDemonMale
racegenders.config_desc: A fiendish heritage results in a half-demon's larger build and horns. Their bloodline may also manifest in other ways including demonic skin-colors and uncanny facial features.

racegenders.name: halfDemonFemale

racegenders.name: halflingMale
racegenders.config_desc: Apart from their larger, pointed ears, halflings resemble tiny, cherubic humans. They often have curly hair and ruddy complexions, and are renowned for their love of food. They are often cheerful and friendly.

racegenders.name: halflingFemale
